* Description
  It is an implementation of Tetris in C++ that uses OpenGL.

* Building
  $ cmake .
  $ make

* Running
  Run the 'nt' binary from the TL source directory, where it expects fonts in './fonts' and
  shaders in './shaders'.

* Dependencies
  SDL2
  FreeType2
  GLEW

* Credits
